Scale_GetBounds
#include Style
#Background wimp 1
Module:	<Scale=>scale/m>
#Line
#Wrap off
Syntax:	Scale_GetBounds
Veneer:	<scale_get_bounds>
#indent

On entry:
#indent 6
{FCode}r0 = flags
     bit 0 - get lower bound.
     bit 1 - get upper bound.
     bit 2 - get step size.
r1 = Scale object ID
r2 = 4
{f}
#indent

On exit:
#indent 6
{FCode}r0 = lower bound value
r1 = upper bound value
r2 = step size value
{f}
#indent
#Wrap
Purpose:	Method gets the bounds for the Scale object.